OL,3,CIran deal 'will be a good deal', says
OL,4,CHegseth as Trump withholds decision
OL,6,FAny deal with Iran will be a "good
OL,7,Fdeal" the US defence secretary said on
OL,8,FSaturday after Donald Trump left a two-
OL,9,Fhour situation room meeting with his
OL,10,Fadvisers without a final decision.
OL,12,FPete Hegseth told an international
OL,13,Fforum on Saturday that Trump was being
OL,14,Fpatient in making sure any peace pact
OL,15,Fwith Iran to ensure that any agreement
OL,16,Fprevents Iran from acquiring a nuclear
OL,17,Fweapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
