OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780229466
OL,3,CIran deal 'will be a good deal', says
OL,4,CHegseth as Trump withholds decision
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Shangri-La Dialogue in
OL,7,FSingapore, Hegseth said: "I had a
OL,8,Fchance to talk to President Trump this
OL,9,Fmorning. He wanted me to reiterate how
OL,10,Fpatient he is in ensuring that with
OL,11,FAmerica undertaking this kind of
OL,12,Fhistoric endeavour, any deal will be a
OL,13,Fgood one, a great one, and he's
OL,14,Fpatient in the pursuit of that."
OL,16,F"If Iran doesn't want to make a great
OL,17,Fdeal that ensures they don't get a
OL,18,Fnuclear weapon," then Iran can "deal
OL,19,Fwith" the US military, Hegseth said.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUxD@AOUzD@PO]zD@`OU{D@EO]
