OL,3,CIran deal 'will be a good deal', says
OL,4,CHegseth as Trump withholds decision
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHegseth said American forces are fully
OL,12,Fprepared to resume military action if
OL,13,Fso ordered, and that weapons
OL,14,Fstockpiles are enough to get the job
OL,15,Fdone.
OL,17,FThe US president held high-level talks
OL,18,Fon Friday but has not yet made a
OL,19,Fdecision on whether to support an
OL,20,Fextension of the ceasefire with Iran
OL,21,Fand reopen the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
