OL,3,CIran deal 'will be a good deal', says
OL,4,CHegseth as Trump withholds decision
OL,6,FWashington officials claimed on
OL,7,FThursday that the US and Iran had
OL,8,Freached a tentative agreement to
OL,9,Fextend the ceasefire. Iran said the
OL,10,Fagreement has not been finalised.
OL,12,FAhead of Friday's meeting, Trump said
OL,13,Fhe was looking to make a "final
OL,14,Fdetermination." A senior
OL,15,Fadministration official later said the
OL,16,Froughly two-hour meeting with national
OL,17,Fsecurity aides had concluded without a
OL,18,Fdecision.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@OO]
