OL,3,CIran deal 'will be a good deal', says
OL,4,CHegseth as Trump withholds decision
OL,6,FTrump wrote on social media that "Iran
OL,7,Fmust agree that they will never have a
OL,8,FNuclear Weapon or Bomb." He said the
OL,9,Fstrait must be reopened for
OL,10,Finternational navigation and all sea
OL,11,Fmines destroyed.
OL,13,FIran's main negotiator said on Friday
OL,14,Fthat it has "no trust in guarantees or
OL,15,Fwords," only actions, underscoring
OL,16,Flingering distrust after the US and
OL,17,FIsrael have twice attacked Iran over
OL,18,Fthe past year while it was engaged in
OL,19,Fnuclear negotiations.
OL,26,@nD@bOUpD@XO]vD@MOUwD@GO]
