OL,3,CIran deal 'will be a good deal', says
OL,4,CHegseth as Trump withholds decision
OL,6,F"No step will be taken before the
OL,7,Fother side acts," Mohammad Bagher
OL,8,FQalibaf wrote on X. "We do not gain
OL,9,Fconcessions through talks, but through
OL,10,Fmissiles."
OL,12,FThe developments came as the fragile
OL,13,Fseven-week ceasefire between the US
OL,14,Fand Iran showed signs of strain, with
OL,15,Fboth sides repeatedly accusing each
OL,16,Fother of violating it in the last few
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@QO]pD@UOU
